{"tid":1100082,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"【令人髮指】兩90後拍「搞笑」片搏點擊 推陌生男落橋累佢溺斃","createTime":"2019-04-10T07:59:47.000Z","updateTime":"2019-04-10T08:20:52.000Z","uid":130626,"like":0,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"af6eea12a41e843b5ca7e7d79cd3af3920ea66da","tid":1100082,"uid":130626,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-10T07:59:47.000Z","msg":"早前美國有少女貪玩推朋友落橋，累對方重傷後，網上近日流傳手機片段，當中一名烏克蘭男子被兩名陌生青年推落橋後溺斃。<br />\n片段中，一名48歲男子身處一間建於聶伯河（Dnipro River）橋上的餐廳，他抓緊欄杆，卻被人不斷拳打，之後更被推落橋，墮入3.6米（12呎）下的河中，最終溺斃。有目擊者聲稱男子被推落橋前與兩名兇手發生口角。<br />\n警方拘捕兩名分別23歲和26歲男子，指兩人承認是為拍攝「有趣」片段，推死者落橋。<br />\n警方怒斥現今為搏點擊率而拍攝殘忍片段的風氣「令人髮指」。<br />\n英國《太陽報》<br />\n<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/e-paper/20190410/large/1554855988_ba14.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fe-paper%2F20190410%2Flarge%2F1554855988_ba14.jpg&h=9e846d1d&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.news.appledaily.com/international/realtime/article/20190410/59470429\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Finternational%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20190410%2F59470429&d=CmE1Ecd1w6veVISTpL%2FBTq%2BgbAIUXjhk7Wr4LW24j58%3D&h=06b87a28\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Finternational%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20190410%2F59470429&h=b0dd4996\" target=\"_blank\">https://hk.news.appledaily.com/international/realtime/article/20190410/59470429</a>"},{"pid":"1e678f05bcca36aa263192d9efa3bc3007529143","tid":1100082,"uid":76420,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-10T08:09:28.000Z","msg":"條友死前個眼神<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"425c2b435b94d352e0d7a8d24193404b66be8f82","tid":1100082,"uid":65429,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-10T08:11:09.000Z","msg":"FAKE NEWS"},{"pid":"81ada02428d8a66c6610970592bdfe457f44307c","tid":1100082,"uid":66686,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score"